erikut tata cara lengkap (end-to-end) sesuai gambar: ALB + SSL (ACM) + Auto Scaling + CloudFront (S3 + ALB) di AWS.

Saya buat urut dari nol sampai jalan.

🧱 1. Persiapan (Wajib sebelum mulai)

Pastikan kamu sudah punya:

VPC (default juga boleh)
Subnet Public & Private (minimal 2 AZ)
Security Group
Aplikasi Node.js kamu sudah siap (port misalnya 3000)
AWS Account aktif
🔐 2. Request SSL Certificate (ACM)

👉 Service: AWS Certificate Manager (ACM)

Langkah:

Masuk ACM
Klik Request Certificate
Pilih: Public Certificate
Masukkan domain:
contoh: api.domainkamu.com
Validation method: DNS validation
Klik request
🔑 Validasi DNS
AWS akan kasih CNAME record
Masuk ke domain provider (Route53 / Niagahoster / dll)
Tambahkan CNAME itu
Tunggu status jadi: ISSUED
🎯 3. Buat Target Group

👉 Service: EC2 → Target Groups

Klik Create Target Group
Pilih:
Target type: Instances
Protocol:
HTTP
Port: 3000
Health Check:
Path: /health
Register target:
pilih EC2 instance kamu (nanti bisa juga Auto Scaling)
🖥️ 4. Buat EC2 (jika belum ada)
Launch EC2 (Amazon Linux / Ubuntu)
Install Node.js + app kamu

Pastikan app jalan:

node app.js
Pastikan security group:
port 3000 open (dari ALB saja)
⚖️ 5. Buat Application Load Balancer (ALB)

👉 Service: EC2 → Load Balancers

Klik Create Load Balancer
Pilih: Application Load Balancer
Setting:
Scheme: Internet-facing
IP: IPv4
VPC: pilih VPC kamu
Subnet: Public A & B
Security Group ALB:
Allow:
HTTP 80
HTTPS 443
Listener default:
HTTP (80)
Target Group:
pilih target group yang sudah dibuat
🔒 6. Setup HTTPS (443)

Masuk ke ALB → Listener

Add Listener:
HTTPS : 443
Pilih SSL Certificate dari ACM
Default action:
Forward ke Target Group
🔁 Redirect HTTP → HTTPS

Tambahkan rule:

HTTP 80 → Redirect ke HTTPS 443
📈 7. Auto Scaling Group (ASG)

👉 Service: EC2 → Auto Scaling

1. Launch Template
AMI: Amazon Linux / Ubuntu
Instance type: t2.micro / t3.micro
User data (install node app otomatis)
2. Buat ASG
Attach Launch Template
Attach ke Target Group
3. Setting Scaling:
Min capacity: 2
Max capacity: 10
4. Scaling Policy:
Scale OUT:
CPU > 70% → tambah 2 instance
Scale IN:
CPU < 30% → kurangi 1 instance
Cooldown: 300 detik
☁️ 8. Setup S3 (Static Asset)

👉 Service: Amazon S3

Create bucket:
contoh: frontend-assets-kamu
Upload:
gambar
css
js frontend
🌍 9. Setup CloudFront (CDN)

👉 Service: Amazon CloudFront

Origin 1: S3
Origin domain: S3 bucket
Untuk static file
Origin 2: ALB
Origin domain: DNS ALB kamu
Untuk API / Node.js app
Behavior CloudFront:
/assets/* → S3
/api/* → ALB
Security:
Enable:
HTTPS Only
Redirect HTTP → HTTPS
🌐 10. Domain (Optional tapi disarankan)

👉 Route53

Create Hosted Zone
Add record:
A record → CloudFront
API record → ALB
🧪 11. Testing

Coba akses:

ALB langsung:
http://alb-dns
https://alb-dns
CloudFront:
https://domain-kamu.com

Cek:

API jalan
SSL aktif
Auto scaling nambah instance
Static file dari S3 cepat
🚨 12. Checklist kalau error
Instance health check healthy?
Port 3000 terbuka di EC2?
ALB security group benar?
ACM status sudah ISSUED?
Target group registered?
🧠 Arsitektur akhir (ringkas)
User
 ↓
CloudFront
 ├── S3 (static frontend)
 └── ALB (API Node.js)
        ↓
   Auto Scaling EC2

